---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About · James Allen Brown">
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p class="lede">
      I'm James. After a decade as a software engineer and engineering
      manager, I now apply those engineering principles (clarity, decoupling,
      predictable failure modes, blameless postmortems) to SRE, crisis
      management, and incident response. Some of what I figure out becomes
      essays here. Some becomes working tools. Some stays in a notebook.
    </p>

    <h2 class="eyebrow">Earlier</h2>
    <p>
      Engineering and operations work across
      <strong>Datadog</strong> (cloud observability),
      <strong>Alchemy</strong> (blockchain developer platform), and
      <strong>Shippo</strong> (multi-carrier shipping for e-commerce).
    </p>

    <h2 class="eyebrow">Reach me</h2>
    <p>
      <a href="mailto:jatobrown@gmail.com">jatobrown@gmail.com</a><br />
      <a href="https://github.com/jato">github.com/jato</a><br />
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jamesallenbrown">linkedin.com/in/jamesallenbrown</a>
    </p>

    <h2 class="eyebrow">Colophon</h2>
    <p class="meta">
      Built with Astro and MDX. Set in
      <a href="https://github.com/undercasetype/Fraunces">Fraunces</a> (display)
      and <a href="https://rsms.me/inter/">Inter Tight</a> (text), both
      self-hosted. The cloud animation is older than this site, ported from
      the 2015 version, with the colors kept and the jQuery removed.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose {
    max-width: var(--measure);
  }

  .prose .lede {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 60, 'SOFT' 50;
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 0.8vw + 1rem, 1.4rem);
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .prose h2.eyebrow {
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .prose p {
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }

  .prose .meta {
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .prose strong {
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>
